The '''Icelandic Sculptors Society''' was established in the Icelandic capital of [[Reykjavík]] in 1972<ref>[http://www.cia.is/inst/3.html CIA.is]</ref> by [[Hallsteinn Sigurðsson]], [[Jon Gunnar Árnason]], [[Ragnar Kjartansson (sculptor)|Ragnar Kjartansson]], [[Þorbjörg Pálsdóttir]] and others. 

